ZH: 我的孙女今年十岁了。
EN: My granddaughter is ten years old this year.

ZH: 她是我唯一的孙女。
EN: She is my only granddaughter.

ZH: 我每周都会去看望我的孙女。
EN: I visit my granddaughter every week.

ZH: 我的孙女很聪明，喜欢画画。
EN: My granddaughter is very smart and loves drawing.

ZH: 我的孙女喜欢在花园里玩耍。
EN: My granddaughter likes to play in the garden.

ZH: 我的孙女很懂事，经常帮我做家务。
EN: My granddaughter is very sensible and often helps me with household chores.

ZH: 我的孙女讨厌吃蔬菜。
EN: My granddaughter hates eating vegetables.

ZH: 我的孙女喜欢去公园骑自行车。
EN: My granddaughter likes to ride her bike in the park.

ZH: 我的孙女爱看动画片。
EN: My granddaughter loves watching cartoons.

ZH: 我的孙女戴着一顶粉色的帽子。
EN: My granddaughter is wearing a pink hat.

ZH: 我的孙女学会了弹钢琴。
EN: My granddaughter has learned to play the piano.

ZH: 我的孙女有一只可爱的小狗。
EN: My granddaughter has an adorable puppy.

ZH: 我的孙女喜欢在花园里捡漂亮的花。
EN: My granddaughter likes to pick pretty flowers in the garden.

ZH: 我的孙女正在学习游泳。
EN: My granddaughter is learning how to swim.

ZH: 我的孙女有一头乌黑的长发。
EN: My granddaughter has long black hair.

ZH: 我的孙女喜欢吃冰淇淋。
EN: My granddaughter likes to eat ice cream.

ZH: 我的孙女是家里的小公主。
EN: My granddaughter is the little princess of the family.

ZH: 我的孙女喜欢跳舞。
EN: My granddaughter likes to dance.

ZH: 我的孙女梦想成为一名科学家。
EN: My granddaughter dreams of becoming a scientist.

ZH: 我的孙女有着一双明亮的大眼睛。
EN: My granddaughter has bright big eyes.
